last_episode_to_air.name: The Eternal Sea
last_episode_to_air.overview: The Bárbara de Braganza is attacked on multiple fronts just as the virus starts spreading and the passengers and crew attempt to procure a vaccine.

name: High Seas
overview: Two sisters discover disturbing family secrets after a string of mysterious deaths occur on a luxury ship traveling from Spain to Brazil in the 1940s.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: As the voyage to Brazil continues, new travelers join the passengers and inexplicable situations give rise to rumors that the ship is haunted.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: When the Bárbara de Braganza sets sail from Argentina to Mexico, Eva joins a mission to root out a scientist harboring a fatal virus on board.

episodes.name: The Albatross
episodes.overview: Two sisters bring a stowaway on board a ship traveling from Spain to Brazil, but the situation turns mysteriously fatal once they are out at sea.

episodes.name: The Rings
episodes.overview: Eva accuses Fernando of lying. When a passenger suddenly confesses to the murder, she and First Officer Nicolás suspect something is being covered up.

episodes.name: Sofía
episodes.overview: After a passenger's life is put in danger, the captain makes a bold decision. Carolina asks her uncle about a woman in a photo. Dimas mourns a loss.

episodes.name: Change of Destination
episodes.overview: Carolina hears shocking claims about her family. Nicolás worries the ship is headed into a storm. The captain's decision spurs Aníbal to take action.

episodes.name: The Storm
episodes.overview: In the midst of a turbulent storm, Dr. Rojas and Eva try to save Nicolás. Sebastián asks Dimas to help him win back Verónica. Luisa makes a discovery.

episodes.name: 527 L.
episodes.overview: The sisters confront their uncle with what they've deduced. Clara and Natalia work together on a cover-up. Eva tells Nicolás about the photo she found.

episodes.name: Three Hours
episodes.overview: Dr. Rojas takes drastic measures to save himself, leaving Eva scrambling. Pierre investigates the staircase death. Sebastián pursues Dimas's fuel idea.

episodes.name: Cain
episodes.overview: On Carolina's wedding day, the Villanueva sisters are forced to face an upsetting truth about their family. Varela begins to suspect Natalia and Clara.

episodes.name: Casandra
episodes.overview: The ship rescues five castaways, including a woman named Casandra, who claims to have intuitive powers. Nicolás helps Eva search for her father.

episodes.name: From the Dead
episodes.overview: When Casandra's stories about ghosts start troubling Carolina, Eva begins investigating the new passenger. Natalia negotiates with Detective Varela.

episodes.name: Is Anybody There?
episodes.overview: Casandra conducts a séance and convinces more people about the presence of a ghost on the ship. Verónica feels conflicted. Natalia worries about Clara.

episodes.name: Change Hands
episodes.overview: Carolina starts to distrust Fernando. Eva attempts to learn more about Rosa Marín as strange events keep occurring. Dimas makes a startling discovery.

episodes.name: The Final Act
episodes.overview: Eva and Nicolás work together to uncover the truth about Casandra. Fernando's denials are met with doubts. Natalia starts discrediting Clara.

episodes.name: The Other Side
episodes.overview: A letter and a new witness create more confusion about Rosa Marín's disappearance. Clara's grief and trauma overwhelm her.

episodes.name: Guilties
episodes.overview: Santiago makes an arrest but Eva, Carolina and Casandra aren't convinced the right suspect has been apprehended. Carlos puts his plan into action.

episodes.name: Love Can Kill
episodes.overview: As the ship pulls into port at Rio de Janeiro, Nicolás searches for the gold, Eva looks for her missing sister and devastating secrets come to light.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: As the voyage to Brazil continues, new travelers join the passengers and inexplicable situations give rise to rumors that the ship is haunted.

episodes.name: New Course
episodes.overview: The Bárbara de Braganza prepares to set sail from Argentina to Mexico but, first, Eva is asked to help undercover agents find a man harboring a virus.

episodes.name: Masks
episodes.overview: When a serious crime occurs aboard the ship, Fabio warns Eva their mission is getting dangerous. Carolina becomes entangled in the mystery.

episodes.name: Groundswell
episodes.overview: As the crimes continue, Eva's involvement raises suspicions. Fabio distrusts Carolina. The crew begins to have doubts about the captain's abilities.

episodes.name: Chasing Shadows
episodes.overview: When Fabio gets detained, Eva tries to find Steve's photograph. Carmen's prisoner attempts an escape.

episodes.name: Locked Up
episodes.overview: Verónica seeks help for the bandaged woman traveling with Carmen. Nicolás wonders why the Bárbara de Braganza changed course. Fabio interrogates Ayala.

episodes.name: The Eternal Sea
episodes.overview: The Bárbara de Braganza is attacked on multiple fronts just as the virus starts spreading and the passengers and crew attempt to procure a vaccine.
